{"id":288996,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/04/global-voices-巴西：采访将遭驱逐的原住民部落/","date":"2013-04-14T04:45:18Z","modified":"2013-04-14T04:45:18Z","title":"Global Voices | 巴西：采访将遭驱逐的原住民部落","content":"<p><div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://vimeo.com/user4567746/aldeiamaracanaenglish\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-403477\" alt=\"The interview, in Portuguese and Guarani, has English subtitles.\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/maracana-interview.png\" width=\"493\" height=\"277\" /></a></p>\n<p>此采访以葡萄牙语和瓜拉尼语进行，有英文字幕。</p>\n</div>\n<p>巴西社运人士Nayana Fernandez<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://lab.org.uk/aldeia-maracana-rios-urban-indigenous-village-in-danger-as-brazils-world-cup-approaches\">访问</a>了原居于里约热内卢马拉卡纳部落（Maracanã Village）的原住民。采访之后几天，这些原住民<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2013/03/25/brazil-violently-ousts-indigenous-village-ahead-of-world-cup/\">遭政府暴力驱逐</a>。</p>\n<p> <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/2013/04/14/12366/#more-12366\">(more…)</a></p>\n<p><span><span>作者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/author/tsavkko/\" title=\"文章导读 Raphael Tsavkko Garcia\">Raphael Tsavkko Garcia</a></span> · <span>译者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/author/neon/\" title=\"文章导读 neon\">neon</a></span></span>  · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2013/03/28/brazil-interview-with-indigenous-community-before-eviction/\" title=\"阅读原文  en\">阅读原文  en</a></span> · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/2013/04/14/12366/#comments\" title=\"则留言\">则留言 (0) </a></span><br />分享: <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.hemidemi.com/user_bookmark/new?title=%E5%B7%B4%E8%A5%BF%EF%BC%9A%E9%87%87%E8%AE%BF%E5%B0%86%E9%81%AD%E9